    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#39;m so tired of the boxed annie chun&#39;s peanut sesame noodles i&#39;ve been making to take to work&#8230;you&#39;ve shown me the light! i had to use lemon juice instead of lime, and i cooked a few too many noodles, but it came out delicious. and i&#39;m certainly happy to have tons of leftovers for the rest of the week.</p>
    </div>

